ZH: 她向我许诺了举办一场盛大的晚宴。
EN: She promised me to host a grand dinner party.

ZH: 他许诺过会帮我修理电视机，但至今未兑现。
EN: He promised to help me fix the television, but he hasn't fulfilled it yet.

ZH: 我们要好好利用这个机会，兑现我们的许诺。
EN: We should make good use of this opportunity and fulfill our promises.

ZH: 这位老板曾经许诺过奖金，但最后没有兑现。
EN: The boss had promised a bonus, but in the end, it wasn't delivered.

ZH: 我爸爸向我许诺买一辆新自行车作为生日礼物。
EN: My dad promised to buy me a new bike as a birthday gift.

ZH: 她向孩子们许诺带他们去游乐场玩。
EN: She promised the children to take them to the amusement park.

ZH: 我遵守许诺，每天早上都会去健身房锻炼。
EN: I keep my promise and go to the gym for exercise every morning.

ZH: 他许诺过将来会为这个社区修建一个图书馆。
EN: He promised to build a library for this community in the future.

ZH: 她向自己许诺努力学习，争取考上理想的大学。
EN: She promised herself to study hard and strive to get into her dream university.

ZH: 老师许诺会给我们更多的练习题来巩固知识。
EN: The teacher promised to give us more practice questions to consolidate our knowledge.

ZH: 他们许诺过会尽快完成这个项目，却一拖再拖。
EN: They promised to complete this project as soon as possible, but they keep postponing it.

ZH: 我会许诺照顾好你的宠物狗。
EN: I promise to take good care of your pet dog.

ZH: 老板向员工许诺加薪，以鼓励他们更努力工作。
EN: The boss promised a salary increase to the employees to encourage them to work harder.

ZH: 她向公众许诺会改变政策，以解决社会问题。
EN: She promised the public to change policies to solve social issues.

ZH: 他们许诺为贫困地区提供更多的教育资源。
EN: They promised to provide more educational resources for impoverished areas.

ZH: 我许诺会尽力保护环境，减少浪费。
EN: I promise to do my best to protect the environment and reduce waste.

ZH: 员工许诺会遵守公司的规章制度。
EN: The employees promised to abide by the company's rules and regulations.

ZH: 她向市民许诺改善交通状况，并建设更多的公共交通工具。
EN: She promised the citizens to improve the transportation system and build more public transportation.

ZH: 他许诺给我一份重要的文件，但迟迟不送来。
EN: He promised to send me an important document, but he hasn't delivered it yet.

ZH: 她许诺过会帮助我准备考试，提供学习资料。
EN: She promised to help me prepare for the exam and provide study materials.

ZH: 老师在开学典礼上许诺会努力培养学生成为优秀的人才。
EN: The teacher promised at the opening ceremony to make efforts to cultivate students into excellent talents.
